data.description: Come check out this 3 bedroom 2 bath pool home in San Fernando.  Located on a quiet street, this home offers an updated kitchen, pool with heater, solar system, large driveway, two-car garage, and more.    The home features two fireplaces, a breakfast nook, carpet, and wood laminate flooring.      The kitchen has newer cabinets and countertops with a stainless steel sink.    The home is easily divided into a duplex situation by closing one door.  The back of the house unit has its own entrance, one bedroom, bath, kitchen, and living area.    The two-car garage also represents an opportunity to build an ADU for additional space or rental income.
